### ==========================================
### 2. REGRAS REGIONAIS (CAPITAL -> CAPITAL)
### Prefixos de 2 dígitos. Mais específicas, devem ganhar das regras de Estado.
### SP Capital (01 a 05) para RJ Capital (20 a 23)
### ==========================================

POST {{HostAddress}}
Accept: */*
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Capital SP para Capital RJ - Promocional Leve",
  "originPrefix": "01",
  "destinationPrefix": "20",
  "minWeightKg": 0.01,
  "maxWeightKg": 5,
  "baseValueAmount": 25.00,
  "currency": "BRL"
}

###

POST {{HostAddress}}
Accept: */*
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Capital SP para Capital RJ - Promocional Médio",
  "originPrefix": "01",
  "destinationPrefix": "20",
  "minWeightKg": 5.01,
  "maxWeightKg": 15,
  "baseValueAmount": 40.00,
  "currency": "BRL"
}


